      "title": "18 hour water cut in Colombo",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the essential maintenance to be carried out at the Ambatalai Water Treatment Plant, this water supply ban will be carried out from 8 am on the 3rd of September until 2 am on the next day on the 4th.",
        "Meanwhile, water supply will be suspended in Colombo, Dehiwela, Kalgissa, Kotte, Kaduwela, Maharagama, Boralaskamuwa, Kolannawa, Kodikawatta, Mulleria, Ratmalana, Katupetha."
      ],
